h1. YARFMP

This is yet another rails flash messaging plugin.  There's tons, I know.  They never work how I want them to.

This one does.

h1. Warning

This is just the first checkin.  It's abstracted from a few projects of mine, and has a bunch of changes
made, but the tests don't work, so I'm sure it's broken.  Don't use it.

